1. Purpose

Provide multi-black-hole initial conditions based on the "puncture" idea:

Steven Brandt, Bernd Br√ºgmann, "A simple construction of initial data
for multiple black holes", Phys. Rev. Lett. 78:3606-3609, 1997, DOI:
